sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server
    participant user

    browser-->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
    activate server
    server-->>browser: Json data
    deactivate server

    user-->>browser: Inserts data to save on server
    browser-->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi//exampleapp/new_note 

    Note right of browser: The browser processes the request getting the input data of the note

    activate server
    server: Process and save the note.
    server-->>browser: [{JSON OF NOTES STORED}]
    deactivate server

    Note right of server: Once its saved the note, the server returns all stored data to the browser.
    browser-->>user: Shows a list of all stored notes, including the one recently added    